<lyrics>[V1]
 ậty ạ̹lyk yạ fạdy ḥyạty yạ mn tzyl kl kẖwfy ậty ạ̹lyk yạ njạty yạ rạfʿy mn kl ḍʿfy)2
 (ạ̹lyk yạ mạnḥ ạlgẖfrạn ạrfʿ nsẖydy ạ̹dẖ qlt ldẖty fy ạlạ̹nsạn ạ̉ʿṭyt mʿny lwjwdy)
